<startofprompt>╭─[{style.MAGENTA}{login}{style.RESET}]~[{style.GREEN}{cdir}{style.RESET}]{nline}╰─►<endofprompt>

styles:
    MAGENTA, BLACK, RED, GREEN, YELLOW, BLUE, MAGENTA, CYAN, WHITE, UNDERLINE, LIGHT
    !! After using color you need to reset it with {style.RESET} !!

syntax:
    !! Prompt should be written in one line. Write it between start and end tokens !!
    {login}    - Current user name
    {mname}    - Machine name
    {cdir}     - Current working directory
    {nline}    - New line
    {style.X}  - X is color of text

Default prompt: ╭─[{style.MAGENTA}{login}{style.RESET}]~[{style.GREEN}{cdir}{style.RESET}]{nline}╰─►